{
  "stem": "7744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I used to think about how I got to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's very interesting that we left the last camp, and we heard already the Russian troops coming from the east.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was the last train that left for Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if we would have just procrastinated instead of getting on this darn train, we would have been liberated by the Russian troops.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and sometimes I think about it, and I think to myself, you know, was my mother more anxious to go with the Germans than stay with the Russians, or didn't she quite comprehend the situation?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, after all, she did come from the German culture, and she always used to say that in a land where the kind of music was composed and the kind of writers and-- and-- and poets lived, this kind of situation can never happen.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I sometimes, when I reflect upon it, I think to myself, why didn't we stay behind?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We heard people say the Russian front is approaching, and-- and-- and-- and the Russian troops were coming in in that direction, because that was already in-- in 19-- in 19-- '40-- '43-- '44-- '44, I think, when we left for Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very interesting, and-- and I sometimes think, you know, we are not very-- very smart as people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, when I think about how we ever ended in the situation such as this, I had an aunt in Canada.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My aunt in Canada came here before the war, and she wanted to bring us over.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
